00021 void printErrorsAndWarnings(MavenCompiler* c) {
00022         if(isErrors(c)) {
00023                 printErrors(c);
00024                 cout << "--- Compilation stopped due to errors" << endl;
00025                 exit(1);

00028         if(isWarnings(c))
00029                 printWarnings(c);
